nodes.text: The Blue Coral Divers Clan was one of the new breed of witch clans on the planet Dathomir. The clan fished for blue corals and allowed both women and men to rule jointly. The Blue Coral Divers feuded with the Scissorfists Clan, another clan that lived near the sea. After years of fighting, both clans tried to settle their differences through a diplomatic meeting. However, the peace talks ended badly and both clans resumed their feud.
